    "mode": "byte_identical",
    "notes": "BigInt is not JSON-serializable, so a portable applet returns BigInt as a string. Exact large-integer arithmetic + BigInt.asUintN/asIntN wrap must be byte-identical (engines historically diverged on very large literals)."
